data.description: ***Huge Price Adjustment! *** BRAND NEW ROOF***Newly Resurfaced Garage Floor*** This can be an easy assumable mortgage with a low interest rate!!!    Step into luxury with this exquisite 5-bedroom, 3-bath home nestled within the desirable gate community of The Estates of Auburndale. Every corner of this home radiates meticulous care and attention to detail. Offering a stunningly renovated interior, this nearly 3000 sq ft abode is the ultimate blend of family comfort and entertainment prowess. Revel in the main living areas' wood-like tile, extending into the master suite for a seamless touch. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, adorned with stone countertops and stainless steel appliances. Energy efficiency is paramount, as the home has been fully sealed and re-insulated. Behold the upstairs space, primed to become your personal movie theater, Large bedroom, giant play room, or spacious retreat. The charming streets on this community lined with majestic oak trees provide a picturesque backdrop for leisurely strolls and bike rides. The community boasts a wealth of amenities including a grand pool, kiddie pool, playground, basketball court, and a serene nature preserve. Strategically situated near I4, this address ensures effortless access to Orlando and Tampa. Elevate your lifestyle - this residence is more than just a home; it's an embodiment of refined living.
